From the DVD jacket - 
The sequel, Bill: On His Own, also starring Mickey Rooney, continues the tale of spirit, strength, and understanding.  While working at a local coffee shop, Bill meets Jenny (Helen Hunt), a sociology graduate student who wants to use Bill as her &quot;class study.&quot;  Jenny discovers that Bill&amp;#039;s achievements cannot be measured by grades or scores, but by his personal growth and his determination to become a regular good man.

Mickey Rooney, Helen Hunt, Edie Mcclurg, Tracey Walter, Teresa Wright

